    </div>
    <div class="section2">
      <div class="container" style="max-width: 640px;margin: auto;">
        <h3 style="text-align: center; color: #6e6e6e; padding-top: 10px; padding-bottom: 7px; font-size: 18.31px;">Thanks for<br>SUBSCRIBING</h3>
        <p style="text-align: left;color: #969696;font-size: 15.69px;">Dear <%= @first_name %>,</p>
        <p style="text-align: left;color: #969696;font-size: 15.69px;">Welcome to On Your Way's travel community !</p>
        <p style="text-align: left;color: #969696;font-size: 15.69px;">On behalf of our team, I'd like to thank you for joining us early on in the project.</p>
        <p style="text-align: left;color: #969696;font-size: 15.69px;">As a gift to our early adopters (that's you!), we will waive our fees on all transactions during the prelaunch period - which amounts to savings of close to 10% on your item requests.</p>
        <p style="text-align: left;color: #969696;font-size: 15.69px;">We'll also take this chance to remind you that posting an item request is totally free and doesn't commit you to anything.</p>
        <p style="text-align: left;color: #969696;font-size: 15.69px;">So you know what to do if you've been missing that lavash that tastes just like home or eager to finally test the ArmPhone !</p>
        <p style="text-align: left;color: #969696;font-size: 15.69px;">Cheers,</p>
        <p style="text-align: left;color: #969696;font-size: 15.69px;">Mane
          <br>CEO at ON YOUR WAY.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

